16
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:49,289
Well I guess it might as well be a Sea Monkey
now.

17
00:00:49,289 --> 00:00:51,530
The program began in 2012.

18
00:00:51,530 --> 00:00:55,390
It was supposed to “adapt existing U.S.
military technologies

19
00:00:55,390 --> 00:01:00,379
