Dragon,

28
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:24,520
or something else.

29
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:25,520
Either way,

30
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,990
the Chinese regime has it now.

31
00:01:26,990 --> 00:01:29,780
I’m sure they’ll put it to good use.

32
00:01:29,780 --> 00:01:32,690
Now there’s good news and bad news to this.

33
00:01:32,690 --> 00:01:33,850
The good news is,

34
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:37,990
