still put it together

37
00:01:46,350 --> 00:01:49,990
to paint an overall picture of US submarine
warfare

38
00:01:49,990 --> 00:01:53,590
that could be considered classified.

39
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:55,240
For example, the Chinese Communist Party

40
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,460
could now know how close a Chinese sub

41
00:01:57,460 --> 00:02:00,970
can get to the US navy before it’s detected.

42
00:02:00,970 --> 00:02:06,240
Whereas before, they had to rely on tactical
dolphins.

43
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,590
Now it’s not really surprising that the
Chinese regime

44
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:10,170
