52
00:02:29,549 --> 00:02:32,609
They also got plans for, “the Black Hawk
helicopter

53
00:02:32,609 --> 00:02:35,790
and the Navy’s new Littoral Combat Ship.”

54
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:38,560
You know what, this is not looking good for
the US military.

55
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:42,489
But I’m sure this is happening because Chinese
military hackers

56
